			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">McCabe Coolidge</span></strong> is a book reviewer, poet, and essayist whose work has appeared in <em>Sail Magazine</em>, the <em>San Francisco Bay Crossing</em>, <em>Dairy Goat Journal</em>, and the <em>New Orleans Review</em>. He once lived on a sailboat in San Francisco Bay but now lives with his sweetheart, Karen, in Greenville, North Carolina, where he makes pottery and skips off to the coast whenever he can to sail, clam, and write.</p><a href="/contributors/mccabe-coolidge" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
